name: First Trust International Capital Strength ETF
longDescription: First Trust International Capital Strength ETF seeks to provide Unitholders with long term capital appreciation by investing primarily in equity securities of developed market companies, excluding the U.S. and Canada, that are traded on global exchanges, with a focus on fundamental strength and growth. To achieve its investment objectives, First Trust Canadian Capital Strength ETF will primarily invest in securities of issuers that are based in Canada or have significant business operations in the Canadian market.
